{"tid":1444501,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[公會戰] Be Water 最大障礙係 RB","createTime":"2019-08-11T12:36:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T14:11:01.000Z","uid":218313,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"c7de5fd2490a08a2d64d822f640998646e9b7f22","tid":1444501,"uid":218313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T12:36:48.000Z","msg":"訓左一個下午,  岩岩起身 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n開左隻ONLINE GAME 黎打<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n下午有公會戰 ,見到好多玩家轉左職做<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">工程師</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n公會戰去到目的地<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">會友話起埋個RB 就轉攻第二個地方</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係DLS <ins><span style=\"color: red;\">好多工程師連絲帽順時定逆時都分唔清</span></ins><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<ins><span style=\"color: red;\">工具又唔齊</span></ins><br />\n攪黎攪去成粒鐘都未攪好一邊RB<br />\n個度成村人等緊你地<br />\n<br />\n唔該工程師下次記得要帶<span style=\"color: red;\"><ins>長身卜頭</ins></span>(唔記得幾號, 好似係10號定12 號), 仲有<span style=\"color: red;\">雙向板手</span><br />\n熟晒點用先出黎打工會戰啦<br />\nLV太低要練下級先得架, 工會會友既性命係晒你地手上!!<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b94292c6a9f39c511d78e18de1b46dba7d08d785","tid":1444501,"uid":218313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T12:40:52.000Z","msg":"推呀<br />\n工程師好緊要"},{"pid":"a07a02d909f7fb8a4d0e9ede51503f2b1a361de5","tid":1444501,"uid":218313,"like":0,